707359f-a.title: Brooklyn: Williamsburg Rd. - Flushing Ave.
707359f-a.text:
Williamsburg Road, north from Flushing Ave. On the right side of
the street in the foreground and background, respectively, is seen the P.S.
Kander Shoe Co., and the J. S. and W. R. Eakins Color Works. A portion of
the U.S. Naval Hos pital is visible on the left side of the street.
September 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
